sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as Dashboard
    participant API
    participant RM as RuntimeManager
    participant Tmux as TmuxRuntime
    participant Reg as SessionRegistry
    participant tmux
    participant Claude

    User->>UI: Click "New session" + keep running
    UI->>API: POST /api/runtime-sessions { persistence: "persistent" }
    API->>RM: create(request)
    RM->>Tmux: create()
    Tmux->>tmux: tmux new-session -d ...
    tmux->>Claude: start claude
    Tmux-->>RM: RuntimeRef
    RM->>Reg: save RuntimeSessionRecord
    RM-->>API: RuntimeRef
    API-->>UI: sessionId
    UI->>API: WebSocket attach
